  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: In different seasons, the Sun appears higher or lower in the sky. In summer,
    the Sun is higher and shadows are shorter. In winter, the Sun is lower and shadows
    are longer. In spring and fall, the Sun is in between, so shadows are of medium
    length. Shadow length changes throughout the year.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
